{"tid":2399602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推動國安法同抗疫防疫agenda有同等份量，中國用緊長春圍城同一招對付香港，黃絲藍絲肯醒未","createTime":"2021-02-08T09:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T09:54:34.000Z","uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98bad60cc42a7623375feeece4e13e03217453a6","tid":2399602,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"【港區政協考核細則曝光】眾新聞得悉，港區省級政協近日首度引入自我考核評分制度，根據眾新聞獲得的評分細則內容，除提案及開會等，參與支持國安法立法街站及聯署、捐贈抗疫物資，或接受採訪或撰寫文章支持國安法立法、押後立法會選舉、DQ民主派議員等逐次計分，要求政協「發揮作用」。<br />\n<br />\n細則同時提及，擔任特區政府諮詢架構成員或授勳，甚至開設Facebook及Youtube，「司法改革、教育改革、傳媒監管」等議題發聲，都有分可加。<br />\n<br />\n有省級政協預計，有關細則是港區省級政協委員聯誼會及中聯辦推動。港區省級政協委員聯誼會會長施榮懷接受查詢時沒有正面回應，只著記者周一辦工時間向秘書處查詢。<br />\n<br />\n【全文閱讀】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3pYs2gj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3pYs2gj&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUim9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=351515bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3pYs2gj</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n【請即訂閱眾新聞，支持中國組】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/訂閲我們\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B2%E6%88%91%E5%80%91&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUim9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=6b47706f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/訂閲我們</a><br />\n訂戶回饋禮：<br />\n・新書《7.1到七一》<br />\n・5張抗爭運動關鍵事件圖解海報<br />\n・兩用帆布袋，以潘源良書法：「寧作飛灰　不作浮塵」為設計<br />\n<br />\n亼 緊貼眾新聞 亼<br />\nMeWe：<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fhkcnews&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUim9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=8df6e639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/hkcnews</a><br />\nFollow TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcnews&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUim9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=cb1f88c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcnews</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykNXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykNXc&d=wu